MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: build the detail in the TSNAP_DTL table for Harvest IDs in the current snapshot
MAPPING.NAME: m_Snap_Hvst_Dtl

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT t1.snap_id ,t1.req_run_ts create_ts ,d.HVST_ID ,d.PERIOD_ID ,d.stat_cd ,d.RPT_ADHOC_STAT_CD ,d.LAST_ALOC_TS from vrap.tsnap t1 ,vrap.tsnap t2 ,VRAP.TSNAP_DTL D WHERE T1.SNAP_RUN_sTAT_CD = 2 --(RUNNING) and t1.period_id = t2.period_id and t1.model_typ_cd = t2.MODEL_TYP_CD and t1.RUN_MODE_CD = t2.RUN_MODE_CD and t2.SNAP_SEQ_NB = -1 -- restrict to current snaps only and t2.snap_id = d.SNAP_ID and d.STAT_CD = 1 -- restrict to only good/active harvests from the current snapshot with ur
